gujarati.context:
Whatever the reason I came, that's what I gained in the end;
When it's necessary to do something, I don't remain the same; 
thus I thought to myself, Great King.

Here is the translation:

His faith follows him in this way, as he said, it is being followed thus;
Birthdays and such rituals are observed, and festival celebrations are done thus.

Here is the translation:

Such a gem-like word this is, it makes the people of the world go mad; 
The bitter fruit that falls from the tree, does not remain with anyone's name.

Here is the translation:

Knowingly serve, serving thusly;
Worshipping, receiving thusly;

Born of noble lineage, a twice-born hero thusly;
Receiving happiness not delayed, Raghuvir thusly.

Here is the translation:

Oh king, I shall remain here, we shall sing; that's what was decided by you, it will be sung;

But in your heart, mind remains, keep our unwritten intention.
